messages.message: Hey team, flagging a disparity in output between Multi-Step & Advanced in Converse when interrogating a long Excel file (6,200 rows). The Advanced model gets all the NY hospitals (which is awesome), whereas the Multistep model taps out very early (which is surprising, because the NY state hospitals are on row ~350, so not that far down the document)
Seems like Multi-step response didn’t go through TDF! cc: @Lalit @Sławek Biel to check this sample. @Will McDermott Can you pls share this doc?
